ETHICAL USE NOTICE

This software is designed for authorized security testing, educational purposes,
and defensive security operations only. Users must obtain explicit permission
before scanning any systems they do not own or have authorization to test.

The authors and contributors are not responsible for any misuse or damage caused
by this software. Use of this tool for attacking targets without prior mutual
consent is illegal and unethical.

By using this software, you agree to use it only for:
- Authorized penetration testing engagements
- Security research with proper authorization
- CTF (Capture The Flag) competitions
- Educational purposes in controlled environments
- Defensive security operations on systems you own or have permission to test

Prohibited uses include but are not limited to:
- Unauthorized access to computer systems
- Denial of service attacks
- Data theft or destruction
- Any malicious activities
- Scanning without explicit permission
